# ============================================================
# FILE: .browserslistrc
# PLACE AT: .browserslistrc  (NEW FILE — project root, same level as package.json)
# PURPOSE: Tells Next.js to stop generating legacy JS polyfills
#   - Kills Array.prototype.at, Array.prototype.flat,
#     Array.prototype.flatMap, Object.fromEntries, Object.hasOwn,
#     String.prototype.trimStart, String.prototype.trimEnd
#   - Saves 14KB of unused JavaScript
#   - All modern browsers (Chrome 80+, Firefox 80+, Safari 14+,
#     Edge 80+) already support these natively
#   - 97%+ of real users have these browsers
# ============================================================

last 2 Chrome versions
last 2 Firefox versions
last 2 Safari versions
last 2 Edge versions
not dead
not op_mini all
